TopicTitle: KSP Space Race: To the Mun in under 20 minutes!!

Articles.Content:
Hey guys! came out with a new video! I was wandering to myself, "Could I get to the Mun in under 20 minutes?" well sure enough I decided to find out! Check it out, and let me know what you think!

Edited December 31, 2014 by Joshdog

Did the pod make it back?

Either way, amazing.
Dude thats amazing! My record was 15 minutes but that was with infinite fuel and a pod with no fuel. Nice Job!

No, there was no attempt to bring it back, The orbit was far out beyond Eeloo if I do remember correctly. Would make for an interesting follow up to try and retrieve it!

- - - Updated - - -

Thanks a lot, It was hard to figure it out but at the end the RCS fuel ended up giving me over 15gs of acceleration when fired!!!
